### Certificates Section
- [ ] Decide on implementation approach
- [ ] Add certificates data to `lib/data.ts`
- [ ] Build UI component
- [ ] Integrate into portfolio

**Implementation ideas:**

**Option A: Toggle with Experience section**
- Add toggle button: "Experience" | "Certificates"
- Reuse timeline/card layout
- Shows one or the other

**Option B: Toggle with Tech Stack section**
- Button to switch: "Tech Stack" | "Certificates"  
- Same section space, different content
- Keeps page length shorter

**Option C: Separate section**
- New dedicated "Certificates & Awards" section
- After Education or Experience
- Most prominent, but adds page length

**Recommendation:** Option B (toggle with tech stack) keeps the page concise while showcasing both skills and credentials.

